            if isinstance(self.password, bytes)
            else self.password
        )', 'advice': "建议定义一个私有方法（如`_ensure_str`）来处理字节到字符串的转换：`def _ensure_str(value): return value.decode('utf-8') if isinstance(value, bytes) else value`，然后在代码中调用`username = self._ensure_str(self.username)`和`password = self._ensure_str(self.password)`。", 'confidence': 0.8, 'relevance': 0, 'severity': 'Low'}]
